score_algorithm(String) - Method in class com.example.qrhunter.generators.QrCodeScoreGenerator
Generates the score of a QRCode by counting repeated characters in a sha-256 hash and adding the sums of the powers of the value of that hash Example: hash = 25cce1b3f4ff0cee487dddddd029041014cf695b85daff02652fab7d308dc802 Repeats: c:2, f:2, e:2, d:6, f:2 Sum repeat values by power-1: 12^1+15^1+14^1+13^5+15^1 = 371349
score_algorithm_test() - Method in class com.example.qrhunter.QrCodeGeneratorsTest
Tests the score algorithm on a few examples done by hand and some edge cases.
